== The green Houses ==
As it stands the 42,000-square-foot health facility located on a 40-acre site next to Mad River Hospital in 
Arcata, California has undergone additional developments. This page specifically gives updates that summarize findings it's local [[community garden]]. Specially, the community garden has provided two additional [[greenhouses]], these were constructed within spring 2013/summer 2013. The materials that compose the green houses are from recycled scraps of wood for structural design and old fans to level humidity levels.
